{"tid":1165511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Jamie Oliver英國連鎖餐廳遭接管　香港Jamie's Italian不受影響","createTime":"2019-05-21T23:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T11:25:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"660cde7a65703538675076db660287068e7e487a","tid":1165511,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:42:39.000Z","msg":"英國名廚、食譜作者及節目主持人Jamie Oliver創辦的、位於英國的25間連鎖餐廳，路透社引述知情人士指出，已在本周二（21日）遭接管，約1300名人手或面臨失業，受影響的25間餐廳中，23間為Jamie's Italian餐廳；本港有兩間Jamie's Italian餐廳，TOPick向其大中華代理查詢，代理指香港和台灣的業務不受影響。<br />\n據路透社消息指出，Jamie Oliver集團旗下的Jamie's Italian連鎖餐廳、以及Barbecoa、Fifteen London等餐廳，已委託畢馬威會計師事務所執行相關清盤程序，並開始為業務尋找新買家，有關決定料於英國時間周二稍後公布，預計受影響員工約有1300人。<br />\nJamie Oliver接受外電訪問時回應表示，對結果感到難過，並向所有職員、供應商表示謝意，又感謝顧客過往的支持。<br />\n香港有三間餐廳，分別是位於銅鑼灣Jamie's Italian、以及位於尖沙咀的Jamie's Italian及Jamie&rsquo;s Deli餐廳，由本港註冊公司「Big Cat Group Limited」（BCG）營運。引入品牌的大中華代理Big Cat Group行政總裁William Lyon回應TOPick指出，香港的業務是獨立於英國，將不受影響；而台灣的Jamie&rsquo;s Deli餐廳情況與香港一樣，也不受影響；他強調，所有業務到目前為止均運作非常順行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2355324/jamieoliver_thumb_20190521_LOK_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2355324%2Fjamieoliver_thumb_20190521_LOK_1024.jpg&h=c3a269cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"417d65bd46ba1bb3cec0632c26a65e7e27519dce","tid":1165511,"uid":200000,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />翻去賣書啦<br />\n<br />\n開餐廳把撚咩，難食到嘔"},{"pid":"b773fb39b334a1ccb1e06ea889d6ed797ea071f4","tid":1165511,"uid":254183,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"660cde7a65703538675076db660287068e7e487a","tid":1165511,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:42:39.000Z","msg":"英國名廚、食譜作者及節目主持人Jamie Oliver創辦的、位於英國的25間連鎖餐廳，路透社引述知情人士指出，已在本周二（21日）遭接管，約1300名人手或面臨失業，受影響的25間餐廳中，23間為Jamie's Italian餐廳；本港有兩間Jamie's Italian餐廳，TOPick向其大中華代理查詢，代理指香港和台灣的業務不受影響。<br />\n據路透社消息指出，Jamie Oliver集團旗下的Jamie's Italian連鎖餐廳、以及Barbecoa、Fifteen London等餐廳，已委託畢馬威會計師事務所執行相關清盤程序，並開始為業務尋找新買家，有關決定料於英國時間周二稍後公布，預計受影響員工約有1300人。<br />\nJamie Oliver接受外電訪問時回應表示，對結果感到難過，並向所有職員、供應商表示謝意，又感謝顧客過往的支持。<br />\n香港有三間餐廳，分別是位於銅鑼灣Jamie's Italian、以及位於尖沙咀的Jamie's Italian及Jamie&rsquo;s Deli餐廳，由本港註冊公司「Big Cat Group Limited」（BCG）營運。引入品牌的大中華代理Big Cat Group行政總裁William Lyon回應TOPick指出，香港的業務是獨立於英國，將不受影響；而台灣的Jamie&rsquo;s Deli餐廳情況與香港一樣，也不受影響；他強調，所有業務到目前為止均運作非常順行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2355324/jamieoliver_thumb_20190521_LOK_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2355324%2Fjamieoliver_thumb_20190521_LOK_1024.jpg&h=c3a269cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0NFk1iJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0NFk1iJ.jpg&h=da046ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df084288d2b86066499678e6d1ef47a6eed794e","tid":1165511,"uid":11523,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:49:36.000Z","msg":"淨係去佢個happy hour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔記得5-6定6-7 $10杯野飲"},{"pid":"153354da4bfc3adef614c4eea24610a2c1788c72","tid":1165511,"uid":242917,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:53:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63f09cd86aa833616f7fc3d68cc5067c803e9915","tid":1165511,"uid":129054,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:58:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d90f0c903361e401b336ec1cab5042110ae231a","tid":1165511,"uid":236646,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote